        <STIG_DATA><VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Rule_Title</VULN_ATTRIBUTE><ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Windows Server 2022 must automatically lock an account when three logon attempts in 15 minutes are made.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA></STIG_DATA>
        <STIG_DATA><VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE><ATTRIBUTE_DATA>The account lockout feature, when enabled, prevents brute-force password attacks on the system.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA></STIG_DATA>
